{"tid":368703,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"lihkg第一屆《清黑頭比賽》*慎入*","createTime":"2017-08-21T17:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T16:01:26.000Z","uid":7923,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85fb50802ceff4caa7bb823c736cd15a17938074","tid":368703,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"好耐以前用過黑頭貼覺得無嘜料到，<br />\n最近心血來潮買盒試下用落男朋友個鼻到。<br />\n睇佢個鼻唔順眼好耐㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清完真係好爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想試嘅話記住最好沖完涼即刻用，因為毛孔擴張咗同啲黑頭軟化咗<br />\n撕起塊貼之後用爽膚水濕化妝棉敷返5分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/011904_5731de32e1db46f84e0cd525594675a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F011904_5731de32e1db46f84e0cd525594675a2.jpg&h=baf45106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e1f2372bfd86414180ef4a18b0aa435d705f88","tid":368703,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"屎"},{"pid":"f67147a280dd7dfc9d0005faf48615ef048d38e5","tid":368703,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屎</blockquote><br />\n屎咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  拎啲黑頭出嚟較量下"},{"pid":"2f1ab25225ab6bbd0e45a363aca2624e397969a2","tid":368703,"uid":136176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"泰國有隻清黑頭仲勁又平先廿蚊<br />\n不過撕出嚟好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96195a784b604ae1cc2bf1a4629f443aeec55cdf","tid":368703,"uid":7923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泰國有隻清黑頭仲勁又平先廿蚊<br />\n不過撕出嚟好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl